<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,1372,1723]" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,273,1516,1542]" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Notes.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng" authorityYear="1998" box="[282,579,1516,1542]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Systolederus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guangxiensis">
<emphasis box="[282,579,1516,1542]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Systolederus guangxiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is not a 
<taxonomicName box="[684,915,1516,1542]" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">
<emphasis box="[684,826,1516,1542]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Systolederus</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
because eyes not draw to each other in front giving the triangular shape to vertex; vertex well depressed, lateral margins of vertex turned backward and elevated up to upper margin of eyes. It belongs to 
<taxonomicName authority="Bolivar, 1817" authorityName="Bolivar" authorityYear="1817" box="[624,857,1588,1614]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Xistra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[624,692,1589,1614]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Xistra</emphasis>
Bolívar, 1817
</taxonomicName>
. We have examined the 
<typeStatus box="[1135,1183,1589,1615]" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">type</typeStatus>
specimens of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng" authorityYear="1998" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Systolederus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guangxiensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Systolederus guangxiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Jiang" authorityYear="1998" box="[423,658,1624,1650]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Xistra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longzhouensis">
<emphasis box="[423,658,1624,1650]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Xistra longzhouensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and found that structures and coloration of the body are the same in both taxa. Therefore, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Jiang" authorityYear="1998" box="[393,627,1660,1686]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Xistra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longzhouensis">
<emphasis box="[393,627,1660,1686]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Xistra longzhouensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is here considered a synonym of of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng" authorityYear="1998" box="[1034,1328,1660,1686]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Systolederus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guangxiensis">
<emphasis box="[1034,1328,1660,1686]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Systolederus guangxiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[= 
<taxonomicName authority="(Zheng, 1998)" authorityName="Zhang &amp; Deng &amp; Li &amp; Lin" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Zheng" baseAuthorityYear="1998" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Xistra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guangxiensis" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">Xistra guangxiensis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Zheng, Z. M." box="[312,459,1696,1722]" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" pagination="161 - 184" refId="ref11163" refString="Zheng, Z. M. (1998) A study of Tetrigoidea from Xishuangbanna (Orthoptera). Acta Zootaxonomica Sinica, 23 (2), 161 - 184." type="journal article" year="1998">Zheng, 1998</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[479,607,1696,1722]" pageId="11" pageNumber="194">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[479,607,1696,1722]" pageId="11" pageNumber="194" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
]
</paragraph>
